name: Chris Gailey
description: I consider myself a person who enjoys life and everything it has to throw at me..I’m loyal and caring and I respect those who respect me back…I don’t have time for petty and selfish behavior or those who believe that the only way to get ahead in life is to downplay their intelligence as if its a virtue…I’m a God-fearing man and a one-woman kind of man…Am an easy going and down to earth type of a man.Am very serious about meeting someone here, I love to swim, beach walking, spend time at home if I have my soul mate around to love and cherish.
